name: 1st Burn - Tempting The Dragon Staff I
description: I met up with a local fire performer group for their weekly practice and asked if I could spin the dragon staff dry without fuel, after getting back into the flow since I last practiced in 2019 the owner of the staff let me light up and it was so warming in the cool weather of Venice CA, what an experience, looking forward to going back again and again! Photo by @bishy.83 on Instagram
